1) Gia na ginei to merging mia epilogh einai to sch-webapps
na ftiaxnei ektelesimo sto .bin:
collection/node_modules/.bin/sch-webapps

O xrhsths 8a etrexe:
npx sch-webapps merging


2) Gia automatopoihsh proteinw h entolh `npx sch-webapps merging`...
na paei sto postinst tou l10759 kai olwn twn allwn.

3) MENU:
O xrhsths trexei p.x. `npx sch-webapps`
Tou emfanizetai menou:

1. Deixe paketa
2. Add paketa
3. Remove paketa
4. merging
5. Start web server
6. Stop web server
0. Quit
